style=\"display:inline-block;width:100%;float:left;\">\n        <p style=\"width:85%;\">\n            \n            <span id=\"ucWebLogin_lblCustomText\"></span></p><div style=\"BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"COLOR: #333333\">You can use Tower Web Payments Center to quickly and securely make your loan payments using funds from another checking or savings account. Whether you have a Tower loan for a car, boat, recreational vehicle, home equity loan, home equity line of credit; or want to make a payment on a personal loan or credit card, you can easily set up web payments here.</span></div>\n<div style=\"BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"COLOR: #333333\">&nbsp;<strong>Important information for first-time users:</strong></span></div>\n<div style=\"BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"COLOR: #333333\">If this is your first time using the Tower Web Payments Center, you’ll need to have the following information in order to register:</span></div>\n<ul>\n    <li>\n    <div style=\"BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"COLOR: #333333\"></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 7pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 115%\">&nbsp;</span><strong><u><span style=\"COLOR: #595959\">Username and Password</span></u></strong><span style=\"COLOR: #595959\">.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"COLOR: #333333\">You will be asked to create a unique username and password to login. You only need to register one time. Use the same credentials to make future online payments.</span></div>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n    <div style=\"BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"COLOR: #333333\"></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 7pt; COLOR: #333333; LINE-HEIGHT: 115%\">&nbsp;</span><strong><u><span style=\"COLOR: #595959\">Member Information</span></u></strong><span style=\"COLOR: #595959\">.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"COLOR: #333333\">To pay via the Web Payments Center, you’ll need to enter the Tower Member Number associated with the loan, as well as your date of birth and the last four digits of your Social Security number.</span></div>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n    <div style=\"BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"COLOR: #333333\"></span><strong><u><span style=\"COLOR: #595959\">Accounts Selection</span></u></strong><span style=\"COLOR: #595959\">.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"COLOR: #333333\">When prompted, please select all of the accounts available—not just the loan you want to initially pay. This will make future payments easier.</span></div>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n<div style=\"BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt 0.25in\"><span style=\"COLOR: #333333\">NOTE: Only primary account holders can register to make payments for Home Equity Line of Credit accounts.</span></div>\n<div style=\"BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"COLOR: #333333\">Other payment options:</span></div>\n<div style=\"BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"COLOR: #333333\">If you're a Tower Home Banking user, make payments by transferring money from your Prime Share savings or checking account to your loan. &nbsp;To pay your Tower Mastercard® account in Home Banking, you have two options. You can make a payment by transferring money to your Mastercard account, or you can select Mastercard to view your account and go to Payments. Follow instructions for payments. </span></div>\n<div style=\"BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt 0.5in\"><span style=\"COLOR: #333333\">Other Ways To Pay: Payment by Mail / In Person Payment / Pay Using Tower Talk 24 / &nbsp;Set Up Automated Payments / Set Up Direct Debit/Credit Payment Authorizations </span></div>\n<div style=\"BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt\"><span style=\"COLOR: #333333\">&nbsp;<strong>If you have problems logging in:</strong></span></div>\n<ul>\n    <li>\n    <div style=\"BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal\"><strong><u><span style=\"COLOR: #595959\">Forgot Your Password</span></u></strong><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #595959\">?</span></strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"COLOR: #333333\">Simply click “Problems Logging In?” (below the Log in button) &nbsp;and follow the directions to reset your password.</span></div>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n    <div style=\"BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal\"><strong><u><span style=\"COLOR: #595959\">Account Lockout</span></u></strong><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #595959\">.</span></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"COLOR: #333333\">Your account will be locked if you have not logged in for 120 days or if five or &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; more failed attempts are made to your account. If your account is locked, you may re-register &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; with a new username (you can use the same e-mail address and Tower Member Number).</span></div>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n            <br>\n            <br>\n            Please log in to begin or register now if you are a first-time user.\n        <p></p>\n        <span id=\"ucWebLogin_lblInvalid\" class=\"warning\"></span>\n        <table style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\" cellpadding=\"0px\" cellspacing=\"2\"> \n            <tbody><tr>\n                <td style=\"font-weight: bold;
